# Kintsugi Environment Variables

# OpenAI API Key (for AI features development & testing)
# Get your key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# IMPORTANT: Never commit your actual .env.local file to git!
NEXT_PUBLIC_OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# Development Notes:
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local
# 2. Replace 'your_openai_api_key_here' with your actual OpenAI API key
# 3. Restart your dev server (npm run dev)
# 4. AI features will now work during development
# 5. Cost: ~$5-20/month depending on testing usage

# For Netlify Deployment:
# Add NEXT_PUBLIC_OPENAI_API_KEY to your Netlify environment variables:
# Site settings > Build & deploy > Environment > Environment variables
